[SN]TITLE[SN]
Fight at Aberdeen theatre during Michael Jackson Thriller Live

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police were called out after a fight broke out at a showing of the Michael Jackson musical Thriller Live in Aberdeen.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened at His Majesty's Theatre (HMT) on Friday evening.
The individuals involved were asked to leave by theatre security staff.
Aberdeen Performing Arts, which operates HMT, said such incidents were rare, and added: "We would like to extend our sincere apologies to anyone who was upset by these events."
